title: #SELFIE (Official Music Video) - The Chainsmokers
description: Check out the music video for The Chainsmokers new single, "Kanye": http://bitly.com/KANYE_MV VOTE for The Chainsmokers DJ Mag Top 100 http://bitly.com/VoteTCSTop100 #SELFIE out now on Dim Mak Records! iTunes: http://smarturl.it/TheChnsmkrsSELFIEiT #SELFIE Tees: http://dmak.co/SELFIE_Merch Beatport: http://bitly.com/SELFIE_Beatport Google Play: http://smarturl.it/ChainsmokersGP When we were creating this video we wanted to gather as many #SELFIE's as we could from friends, fans, celebrities and other types that were willing to take part, so we put in a call for action and received thousands of amazing #SELFIES from so many amazing and funny ppl. Also make sure to make your own #LETMETAKEASELFIE videos and upload them!
